CommentsContent: a lot of people use copier paper in their ink jet printer and then wonder why their printer jams and breaks down early  i have learned the hard way that to get grief free  long life from my ink jet printers  it is best to use ink jet paper  the higher quality results are noticable  there is less dust given off that collects in the mechanism of the printer  and the printer lasts longer but more importantly  when i hand someone a document that i printed on this paper  it is not unusual to hear  oh  you use good paper   that makes me feel good

this is a very reasonably priced general purpose white printer paper   it is  ultra white   and the paper works extremely well with especially hp printers  but probably any printers in terms of clean and accurate feeds and precision results   print quality is very crisp and clean  even photographs reproduce well on this paper   the price is excellent for this level of quality  and a paper of this type should always be used with better inkjet or laser printers made by hp and other manufacturers

i ordered this paper on   july        the paper is now about     gone   i am writing this review now because just today i was reloading my printer and thought   wow  this has lasted a long time  i should write a review  this is plain old paper  nothing fancy or sleek  but it is all you need in this day and age   if you want high quality paper  it is usually to take a resume to an interview or job fair or because you have a sales proposal or something else to provide a customer   the rest of what we print is usually just for editing  off screen  before we submit something electronically  for this type of printing the paper  and the value  cannot be beat in the past year and a half  this box of paper has helped my family as follows  i was able to edit my doctoral dissertation   though each chapter was submitted online  i had to edit them before submitting and i felt compelled to read my professor s comments  also provided online  on a printed document  the same goes with what i submitted to my dissertation committee   when the final submission was provided  i had to do a complete review before i submitted it  lordy  i did a lot of printing  my son was able to edit his college application essays  so he could edit them before submitting them online    so far  he has one college acceptance letter and is awaiting word from four more universities  our three kids printed all their class assignments  all in high school last year  my step daughter now attending community college    and more  i am sure again  given that most of us still need to read a hard copy document to edit  this paper is great oh  i ve read that a lot of folks with the lower ratings received their box in bad shape  so their problem was with the packaging   my box arrived in great condition and even if it hadn t  i have other boxes and bins i could have stored this paper in   that s why i was willing to take the chance and order it one and a half years later  i am still glad i did
